@Frogsterking: See your <a href="https://forum.mafiascum.net/viewtopic.php?p=3599362#p3599362" class="postlink">647</a>.  Elaborate on your reads, I don't care how uninteresting.  If both Hikari Link and Guy_Named_Riggs are mafia, why change your vote?<br>
